title: Rep. Buck, Google Lawsuit, Nashville Debate
itunes:title: Rep. Buck, Google Lawsuit, Nashville Debate
description:
Guests: David Balto, former policy director of the FTC bureau of the competition, and former trial attorney at the DOJ Antitrust Division, Robert Shapiro, Chairman of Sonecon, Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative media, Tyler Deaton, Republican strategist, fundraiser, and President of Allegiance Strategies, and Rep. Ken Buck, a Republican representing Colorado's 4th congressional district. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
